{"tid":787941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估地方) 不滿睡覺被鬧　少年持刀砍好友3刀","createTime":"2018-08-21T05:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T17:49:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f497a150782d1b68b5f7df9d6dda19c82ac7c397","tid":787941,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"新北市三重區三和路四段上，今天凌晨發生一起砍人案件。4名未成年的少年在家中喝酒，其中1名陳姓少年因不勝酒力，先去房間內休息睡覺，另外3名少年竟趁他在睡覺時不斷地搖他，還在他耳朵旁大叫，在睡覺的陳少被吵得受不了，一時惱怒竟拿觀賞用的獵刀，朝其中一名吳姓少年砍去，造成他臉部及左手多處刀傷，所幸送醫急救並無大礙，警方事後將砍人的陳少帶回問訊。<br />\n警方調查，被砍的17歲吳姓少年，今天凌晨1時許，與3名友人三重區三和路一處民宅喝酒，其中17歲的陳姓少年因不勝酒力，直接走回房間內睡覺，吳少與另2名朋友則繼續在客廳飲酒作樂，直到凌晨3時許，吳少向2名友人提議，不要再讓陳少睡覺，3人便決定一起進入房間內要將陳少搖醒。<br />\n過程中，陳少因被吵得受不了，多次要朋友不要再鬧他，讓他繼續睡覺；但3人仍不停手，吳少甚至還在他耳朵邊大叫：「起床了！不要再睡覺了！」不叫還好，這一叫惹得陳少抓狂，看見衣架旁有一把觀賞用獵刀，拿了就直接朝吳少砍過去，造成對方臉部及左手3處刀傷，另2名友人見狀，才立即上前制止。<br />\n由於吳少流血過多，一旁的朋友見狀立即報警，警消到場後，先將吳少傷口包紮，並送往台北市新光醫院縫合，所幸並無生命危險。警方到場後，也立刻將砍人的陳少帶回派出所問訊。（突發中心潘志偉／新北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/134031_8b07191c37e85b2e77b3b0fc3a230b47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F134031_8b07191c37e85b2e77b3b0fc3a230b47.png&h=604b8f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/134037_343278c50595e794d8a72bbb058cfe0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F134037_343278c50595e794d8a72bbb058cfe0f.png&h=99b46d4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180821/1414744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180821%2F1414744&d=ogEaDYtAKoEXuTJTj9L6Uv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=58389af8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180821%2F1414744&h=64526596\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180821/1414744</a>"},{"pid":"5315e1683063d5887ef5aaa4f3595816988946af","tid":787941,"uid":4440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"Goal!"},{"pid":"43916bc6d173ea11eb9d8dcac5c74c3da852a378","tid":787941,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中左"},{"pid":"9a02fac2bc58bf40c70bb8b39a4bffc4063d6965","tid":787941,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43916bc6d173ea11eb9d8dcac5c74c3da852a378","tid":787941,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:11:45.000Z","msg":"點解會估新北？"},{"pid":"127f1255f0c9cead15c44e32e7aedd31c620233b","tid":787941,"uid":186155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4873c80f3defbb94c975ade0b4f9d148aea0e161","tid":787941,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43916bc6d173ea11eb9d8dcac5c74c3da852a378","tid":787941,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}